<BaseLayout title="About GameHelp India" description="GameHelp India is an independent consumer-safety information portal for online-game payment, account and APK issues." canonicalPath="/about/">
<main id="main"><article class="prose"><span class="kicker">Independent consumer information</span><h1>About GameHelp India</h1><p>GameHelp India helps users organise evidence and find safer escalation steps when an online-game deposit, withdrawal, account or APK issue occurs.</p><h2>What we do</h2><ul><li>Explain how to preserve transaction evidence.</li><li>Provide neutral complaint and escalation checklists.</li><li>Warn against fake customer care, OTP theft and remote-access scams.</li><li>Link to official Government of India cybercrime resources.</li></ul><h2>What we do not do</h2><ul><li>We do not operate or represent gaming apps.</li><li>We cannot release withdrawals or credit deposits.</li><li>We do not accept money, OTPs, KYC documents or banking access.</li><li>We do not distribute APK files or real-money game referral links.</li></ul><h2>Emergency fraud reporting</h2><p>For suspected cyber financial fraud, call <strong>1930</strong> and use <a href="https://cybercrime.gov.in/" rel="noopener noreferrer">cybercrime.gov.in</a>.</p></article></main>
</BaseLayout>
